Package utils.Receipt.CustomReceiptItems

Class NodePrinter.PrintInfo

java.lang.Object
utils.Receipt.CustomReceiptItems.NodePrinter.PrintInfo
Enclosing class:
NodePrinter
public static class NodePrinter.PrintInfo extends Object
Encapsulates information for printing with a specific PageLayout, i.e. the scale dependent on the screen DPI as well as the number of rows and columns for poster printing.
